{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/til/shell/direnv/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"bestalign's dev blog","categories":[{"displayText":"홈","priority":0,"name":"home","url":"/"},{"displayText":"TIL","priority":1,"name":"til","url":"/til"},{"displayText":"개발","priority":2,"name":"dev","url":"/dev"},{"displayText":"독서","priority":3,"name":"reading","url":"/reading"},{"displayText":"번역","priority":4,"name":"translation","url":"/translation"},{"displayText":"일기","priority":5,"name":"everydaylife","url":"/everydaylife"}]}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"cba9ac1c-70a7-5285-86a1-3e36fa1b769b","excerpt":"는 각 디렉토리마다 환경변수를 다르게 설정할 수 있는 기능을 제공한다. 여러 프로젝트를 동시에 진행할 때 프로젝트마다 AWS Token이나 다른 환경변수가 다른 경우가 있다. 를 사용하면 프로젝트마다 다른 환경변수를 사용하는 것이 가능하다. Install direnv Configure…","html":"<p><code class=\"language-text\">direnv</code>는 각 디렉토리마다 환경변수를 다르게 설정할 수 있는 기능을 제공한다. 여러 프로젝트를 동시에 진행할 때 프로젝트마다 AWS Token이나 다른 환경변수가 다른 경우가 있다. <code class=\"language-text\">direnv</code>를 사용하면 프로젝트마다 다른 환경변수를 사용하는 것이 가능하다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"install-direnv\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#install-direnv\" aria-label=\"install direnv permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install direnv</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token comment\"># install on mac</span>\n$ brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> direnv</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"configure-shell\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#configure-shell\" aria-label=\"configure shell permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Configure shell</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token comment\">## BASH -> ~/.bashrc에 아래 내용 추가</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">eval</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span>direnv hook <span class=\"token function\">bash</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">## ZSH -> ~/.zshrc에 아래 내용 추가</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">eval</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span>direnv hook <span class=\"token function\">zsh</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"configure-direnv\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#configure-direnv\" aria-label=\"configure direnv permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Configure .direnv</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> project_dir\n$ <span class=\"token function\">touch</span> .envrc\n<span class=\"token comment\"># update .envrc</span>\n$ <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">'export HELLO=world'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span> .envrc\n$ direnv allow</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.44bits.io/ko/post/direnv_for_managing_directory_environment\">44Bits - direnv</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.outsider.ne.kr/1306\">Outsider’s Dev Story - 폴더별 환경 관리를 위한 direnv</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/direnv/direnv\">Github - direnv</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"direnv - 폴더별 환경관리","category":"til","date":"July 05, 2021","updated":null,"description":null,"tags":["shell"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/til/technical-writing/one/08-paragraphs/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"테크니컬 라이팅 - Paragraphs"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/til/technical-writing/one/09-audience/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"테크니컬 라이팅 - Audience"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"cba9ac1c-70a7-5285-86a1-3e36fa1b769b","previousPostId"